Hello and welcome on my homepage <big>🙋🏾</big>!



I am currently a PhD student at [UQAM](https://uqam.ca) in the [Sociology Department](https://sociologie.uqam.ca). I study internet studies, game studies, and gender. In particular, I am interested in female gamers who streams their games on plateforms like Twitch, and Facebook Gaming. I am actually working of how gender impacts games and game players. 



